          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1720089574915-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>mayo </strong>with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, a squeeze of <strong>lemon juice</strong> and a pinch of <strong>pepper </strong>in a bowl – this is your<strong> lemon aioli</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>in 500ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[650ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[1L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1720089578502-x200.jpg",
