            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once crisped, add the <strong>diced onion </strong>and <strong>pepper strips</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to soften</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1720089585255-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1720089585255-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1720089585255-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1720089585255-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1720089585255-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add the <strong>remaining chopped garlic</strong> to the pan with your <strong>ground smoked paprika </strong>and <strong>tomato paste</strong> and cook for 1-2 min or until fragrant</p><p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>orzo</strong> and stir to coat the grains in the spices, then add the <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>stock</strong> to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until cooked through (stir the orzo occasionally to stop it from sticking!)</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1720089589648-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1720089589648-x400.jpg",
