            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, stir through your <strong>blanched peas</strong> and cook<strong> </strong>for a further 1 min or until warmed through – this is your <strong>Spanish-style chorizo orzo</strong></p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Tip: Cooking for kids? Add half your blanched peas to a colander,</span></strong> <strong><span class=\"text-danger\">pour boiled water all over them to refresh them and leave plain!</span></strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1720089593498-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1720089593498-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
